creator: PreVet AB
descriptionHtml:
Now you can have everything about the stable and your animals with you in your pocket - wherever you are!

PreVet's app helps you gather and update all the information about your horses, dogs and cats in one place. PreVet is also available for stables and businesses. The app makes it easy for everyone to keep track of the latest health and care information - and together with specialists, such as veterinarians, when something has happened.

With PreVet, you reduce unnecessary misunderstandings and risks, reduce costs, increase profitability and improve animal health!

DIFFERENT ANIMAL TYPES AND ALSO FOR STABLES
You can choose to have several animal species in the app - but only those you have selected will show. If your stable uses PreVet Stall, the collaboration will be even smoother.

PLAN EVERYDAY LIFE
By documenting the animals' everyday lives in a flexible way, you get a good overview of activities and details about both health and care. Everything is saved on a timeline and is easy to find.

IMPROVED DIALOGUE WITH VETERINARY AND OTHER SPECIALISTS
When contacting a veterinarian, you have all the information in your mobile and can easily view the animal's profile and medical history for the veterinarian directly in the app. The overall documentation in turn means that the veterinarian receives the correct information for the assessment and reduces the risk of misunderstandings.

FORGET NOTHING IMPORTANT
With PreVet's app, you do not risk forgetting the important things in everyday life that concern your animals. The app provides reminders about vaccinations, ultrasound, medication, treatments, deworming and everything else you want to remember.

DEEPEN YOUR KNOWLEDGE
Build on your knowledge with Sweden's foremost experts. In the app, you get tips and links directly in the inbox - which helps you take care of your animals in the best way.
descriptionShort: Reduce your costs and improve your animals’ everyday life with the PreVet app!

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Now we have opened the app for all horses too, welcome!
You can also share information about your animal, for example, to a family member, fellow trainer or veterinarian.
